[DVD-R]Cat Stevens - Majikat(Show)

Majikat is a live album and DVD by British singer/songwriter Cat Stevens. It was recorded during the US leg of Stevens&#039; Earth Tour 1976, but was not released until 2004, by which time the artist was known as Yusuf Islam.
